      "widgets_values": [
        "# prompts that worked\n\n## i2v:\n\nsingle image in image_0\n\n```\nYou are a helpful assistant specialized in text-to-video generation.\n\nFrom image_0 the woman performs a high-energy cheerleader dance routine. She executes a high jump, then a cartwheel across the stage. Her ponytail bounces with the movement. She does a high kick toward the front of the stage, followed by the splits at the back of the stage, clapping her hands above her head once. Fast-paced, highly energetic. Smooth, fluid motion. She stays on the theatre stage the entire time.\n```\n\n```\nYou are a helpful assistant specialized in text-to-video generation.\n\nFrom image_0 cinematic long shot, smooth continuous orbiting camera rotating steadily around the subjects. The camera circles the scene in a fluid 360-degree arc. Three nymphs playfully interact with a satyr, gathered around a rocky pool at a cascading waterfall. 19th-century French academic oil painting style, William-Adolphe Bouguereau aesthetic, lush forest background, soft dappled sunlight, masterpiece, highly detailed, realistic lighting, steady camera motion, high temporal consistency, no morphing, 5-second continuous shot.\n```\n\n"
      ],
